{"tid":1515390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唓，放流料就係到互相指責","createTime":"2019-08-29T06:32:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T08:27:00.000Z","uid":58434,"like":19,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"079738c106b58ccc74784f17d8bf3255e09162e8","tid":1515390,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:32:30.000Z","msg":"放流料實係自己友咩?<br />\n唔俾係對家做嘅?<br />\n對家信用都破哂產啦，唔爭在用埋D下九流嘅手段污染連登<br />\n前線都有鬼扮示威者,何況連登?<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 大家記住指責無用,</span></strong></span><br />\n呢個月黎連登印象分係增加唔少<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">只因為連登係證據嘅平台，緊守呢個宗旨</span></span><br />\n我地唔好因為呢單嘢再指責不是，非事實就冷處理就得啦<br />\n真實係要比公眾知道"},{"pid":"8ec68a7d072313ffa7b9ddabbf56efdef7b1f96c","tid":1515390,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:33:16.000Z","msg":"齊手守護證據嘅平台"},{"pid":"a04e49ed963db9fd8a5b6c69f914279c844c0a31","tid":1515390,"uid":58434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:33:28.000Z","msg":"齊手守護證據嘅平台"},{"pid":"27cd7d902eb02a331609275c0493beddc98eb050","tid":1515390,"uid":273916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-29T06:33:31.000Z","msg":"唔好意思借個post宣傳一下<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3J6Zqr9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3J6Zqr9.jpg&h=398279dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/OTykUks.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOTykUks.jpg&h=e262c427&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vD12Zp3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvD12Zp3.gif&h=f9a83f22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GcUsmkJ.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGcUsmkJ.gif&h=2a4b8943&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/P7Tdf8O.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"ht